Name: Jetpack Guy
About the game: Can We Go to the Top? This TV-Headed Guy Want to fly High with His Jetpack! What Does He Want to do After Climbed to the Top? Check His Action With Your Eyes! There are Many Annoying Obstacles that stand in Your Way. Watch his Head! He will be fainted when He get the impact on His Head! Your Fuel is Limited per Flight. You must rest on Floor When Fuel is Empty. So, Be careful! Fly to the Top with this Jetpack!
